$	Line {L_5 = P_4_P_6 = lc++} goes from Point {P_4} to Point {P_6}
$	Line {L_6 = P_6_P_5 = lc++} goes from Point {P_6} to Point {P_5}
$	Line {L_7 = P_5_P_3 = lc++} goes from Point {P_5} to Point {P_3}

$
$ Regions: {rc = 1} (region counter)
$	Region { R_1 = rc++ } circumscribed by lines {L_1}, {L_2}, {L_3}, {L_4}
$	Region { R_2 = rc++ } circumscribed by lines {L_3}, {L_5}, {L_6}, {L_7}
